{"tid":768124,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"教大家點樣賺大錢","createTime":"2018-08-05T06:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T13:36:15.000Z","uid":17088,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8695f846e19e77dccd8aa24af8f8f3dfe5c18dd9","tid":768124,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:25:30.000Z","msg":"首先 搵一個partner <br />\n大家努力返工分別儲錢儲返十零廿萬先<br />\n<br />\n然後搵一間細鋪 唔洗喺正旅遊區 但要易去<br />\n例如天后 (去開銅鑼灣既人會去), 佐敦 (近尖沙咀)<br />\n呢啲地方鋪租相對平少少 但人流都夠<br />\n而且唔喺最大路既地方啲人就可以話俾人知<br />\n&ldquo;嗱 我幾識食! 咁都俾人搵到呢間嘢呀!&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解要細? <br />\n因為要俾人排隊營造好多人食既錯覺<br />\n香港人最鍾意就係排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後諗一樣好值得影相既食物/飲品<br />\n好唔好食唔緊要 最緊要成本夠低+影出嚟靚<br />\n然後賣比成本貴50倍價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人最鍾意俾錢食貴嘢嚟突顯自己有錢<br />\n要話俾人聽咁貴咁唔值我都食得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n俾錢搵kol影幾張相 開返幾個打手post<br />\n整返個vip system 送俾啲kol <br />\n等大家都好想同班kol一樣做到vip <br />\n覺得自己高級過人<br />\n但其實都係啲小恩小惠<br />\n例如買十送一咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁班傻仔就會屌完又翻屌 屌完又翻屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講咁耐我都係努力返工儲吓錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f728197e95a650545dd21ffc7de87b99c195cf","tid":768124,"uid":68589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"賣貴50倍都應該有一半去左交租<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2816a52e7a254894a6fa05457346805d9d44deac","tid":768124,"uid":166827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"啲野食要叫超邪惡隱世加埋芝士，大把港女搶住食，貴成本百倍都得，到時發過豬頭"},{"pid":"ac71947b55e25bdc8fde7201d108e4a9e655459d","tid":768124,"uid":17088,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"30f728197e95a650545dd21ffc7de87b99c195cf","tid":768124,"uid":68589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"賣貴50倍都應該有一半去左交租<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:54:10.000Z","msg":"當賣珍珠奶茶<br />\n自己同partner自己做+請2個part time<br />\n減材料成本拉返平均一杯應該都賺20<br />\n一個落單 3個整茶<br />\n一分鐘賣3杯 當一日有4個鐘忙到唔停手<br />\n已經$14,400 當開10-12個鐘<br />\n一日應該有20k生意額<br />\n一個月就600k<br />\n鋪租check過600呎左右既話就40-50k/month<br />\n減返燈油火蠟 人工 廣告費 100k<br />\n一個月都起碼賺400k<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港人貪新鮮 3個月後應該生意額會下滑<br />\n但已經賺到fapfap可以離場了"},{"pid":"0a284225f94a5dc70c00195fd70c558110dbccc1","tid":768124,"uid":30090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"講到咁易你唔去實行？"},{"pid":"2c09e701b91f8962cecd355e252dc9fe72d1908c","tid":768124,"uid":190066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cde02075c8bc2118037a94997704fd1bb204355","tid":768124,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a284225f94a5dc70c00195fd70c558110dbccc1","tid":768124,"uid":30090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"講到咁易你唔去實行？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T07:03:48.000Z","msg":"儲撚緊錢囉咪"},{"pid":"e34f3e23e42bb911459e16c7b92dae4559467329","tid":768124,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T07:03:49.000Z","msg":"屌你唔洗交租呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45fbb8dbe2009d581397bc7ef2d75541295b8de","tid":768124,"uid":17088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e34f3e23e42bb911459e16c7b92dae4559467329","tid":768124,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T07:03:49.000Z","msg":"屌你唔洗交租呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"盲都識上連登<img src